- Out of scope: packages/server/ unless explicitly asked.

## Current APIs
- GET /api/dashboard/kpis, /dashboard/profit-summary, /dashboard/activity, /dashboard/status
- GET /api/vat/calculate

## Two modes
- Overview: Full dashboard with KPIs, quick tools, profit summary
- Sidecar: Shows QuickCheck (compact price check + landed cost + inventory awareness)

